        "title": "Economic empowerment\n",
        "story": {
            "storage": "WEBAPP",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "title": "<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#FF8C00;\"><strong>Economic empowerment</strong></span></span></p>\n",
                    "content": "<style type=\"text/css\">    p,\n    h1,\n    h2,\n    h3,\n    h4,\n    h5,\n    li {\n        margin-bottom: 2em;\n    }\n\n    .sidePanel .content {\n        font-size: 13px;\n    }\n\n    title {\n        font-size: 40px;\n        line-height: 1.6;\n\n    }\n\n    .methodology {\n        margin: 10px;\n        padding: 40px 20px 20px 20px;\n        background-color: rgb(255, 206, 151);\n    }\n\n    .definition {\n        font-weight: 600;\n    }\n\n    .footnote-index {\n        vertical-align: super;\n        font-size: 0.7em;\n        margin-left: 2px;\n        color: #FF5733;\n    }\n\n    .section a[data-storymaps] {\n        border-bottom: none !important;\n        text-decoration: none;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        color: #FF5733;\n    }\n\n    /* This is based on https: //www.sitepoint.com/accessible-footnotes-css/ */\n\n    .footnotes {\n        border-top: 1px solid #555;\n\n        font-size: 0.9em;\n    }\n\n    .references {\n        font-size: 0.9em;\n    }\n</style>\n<div class=\"title\">Canada: gender wage gap</div>\n",
                    "contentActions": [],
                    "creaDate": 1602482990525,
                    "pubDate": 1602482990525,
                    "status": "PUBLISHED",
                    "media": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "image": {
                            "url": "https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/cdf24c9c28b94260a4917cf5211cb321/resources/sam-manns-p0ZvBVpW3KY-unsplash__1602482987709__w1200.jpg",
                            "type": "image",
                            "altText": "",
                            "sizes": [
                                {
                                    "name": "sam-manns-p0ZvBVpW3KY-unsplash__1602482987709__w1200.jpg",
                                    "url": "https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/cdf24c9c28b94260a4917cf5211cb321/resources/sam-manns-p0ZvBVpW3KY-unsplash__1602482987709__w1200.jpg",
                                    "width": 1200
                                }
                            ],
                            "display": "fill"
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "title": "<span style=\"font-size:26px;\">Key points</span>",
                    "content": "<ul class=\"key-points\">\n<li>Canada\u2019s gender wage gap was 13.3% in 2018, an improvement of 5.5 percentage points from 1998.<span class=\"footnote-index\">1</span></li>\n<li>Between 1998 and 2018, 26.3% of the narrowing in the gender gap came from changes in women's and men's occupations.</li>\n<li>In 2018, 39.7% of the gender wage gap was due to the effect of women and men being employed in different industries, with three high-paying, male-dominated sectors driving the gap in wages: construction; manufacturing; and mining, quarrying and oil and gas extraction. In addition, a significant portion of the gap (9.2%) was the result of women\u2019s higher rate of part-time work, which had lower average wages than full-time work.</li>\n<li>About two-thirds of the gender wage gap was driven by unexplained factors, including work experience, or unobservable factors, for example, gender-related biases.</li>\n</ul>\n",
                    "contentActions": [],
                    "creaDate": 1602483409111,
                    "pubDate": 1602483409111,
                    "status": "PUBLISHED",
                    "media": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "image": {
                            "url": "https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/cdf24c9c28b94260a4917cf5211cb321/resources/aditya-das-RNpjzwDBsEY-unsplash__1602483407184__w1200.jpg",
                            "type": "image",
                            "altText": "",
                            "sizes": [
                                {
                                    "name": "aditya-das-RNpjzwDBsEY-unsplash__1602483407184__w1200.jpg",
                                    "url": "https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/cdf24c9c28b94260a4917cf5211cb321/resources/aditya-das-RNpjzwDBsEY-unsplash__1602483407184__w1200.jpg",
                                    "width": 1200
                                }
                            ],
                            "display": "fill"
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "title": "<span style=\"font-size:28px;\">In 2018, women in Canada earned, on average, 87 cents for every dollar earned by men</span>",
                    "content": "<p>In Canada, women in the core working ages (ages 25\u201454) earned an average of $26.92 per hour in 2018, while their male counterparts earned $31.05 per hour.<span class=\"footnote-index\">2</span> In other words, women earned $4.13 (or 13.3%) less per hour, on average, than men, or $0.87 for every dollar earned by men. Understanding the impacts of various factors on the gender wage gap, and its change over time, contributes to broader efforts to monitor the gender-based pay disparity in Canada, and could point the way towards relevant policy interventions.</p>\n",
                    "contentActions": [
                        {
                            "id": "MJ-ACTION-1598609558915",
                            "type": "navigate",
                            "index": 8
                        }
                    ],
                    "creaDate": 1602483341284,
                    "pubDate": 1602483341284,
                    "status": "PUBLISHED",
                    "media": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "image": {
                            "url": "https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/cdf24c9c28b94260a4917cf5211cb321/resources/david-todd-mccarty-VGLImIsgs9A-unsplash__1602483030510__w1200.jpg",
                            "type": "image",
                            "altText": "",
                            "sizes": [
                                {
                                    "name": "david-todd-mccarty-VGLImIsgs9A-unsplash__1602483030510__w1200.jpg",
                                    "url": "https://www.arcgis.com/sharing/rest/content/items/cdf24c9c28b94260a4917cf5211cb321/resources/david-todd-mccarty-VGLImIsgs9A-unsplash__1602483030510__w1200.jpg",
